<p><strong>System » Settings » Editors</strong></p>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
<h2 id="_areas">1. Areas</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The <strong>Editor</strong>, <strong>Syntax editor</strong> and <strong>Text field</strong> are activated in all areas by default. However, they can be deactivated in individual areas. Go to <strong>System » Settings » Editors » Tab: Areas</strong> and choose which editors should be displayed in the drop-down menu within each specific area.</p>
</div>
<div class="imageblock">
<div class="content">
